# MODE B — STEP 7: MAGNETIC DESIGN (Reference Step 13)
# STEP 8: TIME-DOMAIN CORE-LOSS MODELING (Reference Step 14)
#
# HITL flow:
#   Gate 1 → GET  /mode-b/step7/material-comparison   (Ferrite vs Powder)
